Package grafioschtrader.service

Class GTNetLastpricePoolService

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.service.GTNetLastpricePoolService
@Service public class GTNetLastpricePoolService extends Object
Service for managing the GTNet lastprice push pool. Provides unified methods for updating the push pool (GTNetInstrument* + GTNetLastprice tables) from various sources:
  • Connector-fetched prices (Security/Currencypair entities)
  • Pushed prices from remote servers (InstrumentPriceDTO)
  • Prices received during exchange requests (InstrumentPriceDTO)
All methods follow the same pattern:
  1. Find or create GTNetInstrument entry
  2. Find or create GTNetLastprice entry
  3. Update only if the new price has a newer timestamp
